{"tid":1449554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:19.000Z","uid":268250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1daadd9d59177af0d822052313f821e8f096c14c","tid":1449554,"uid":268250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpoLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=30564f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpoLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=eb6da238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"6bd0172bcac462a826440428ae54505d463e2271","tid":1449554,"uid":268250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7e87cba735ed0c9c027b21385b91986008a8bc7","tid":1449554,"uid":268250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca218c24d2ddbc0e6e9e4153cefa541b2fa93184","tid":1449554,"uid":268250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep